1. docker network create appnet
2. build docker for:
    - apps
        - radar-mandiri-sukses
        - anugrah-travel-api
    - services
        - mysql
        - phpmyadmin
        - nginx

(no need to do this again because already covered by dockerfile)
3. install vendor
docker exec -it php-ci4-rms bash
composer install

(no need to do this again because already covered by dockerfile)
4. set permission
docker exec -it php-ci4-rms bash
chown -R www-data:www-data writable/cache
chown -R www-data:www-data writable/session
chown -R www-data:www-data writable/logs

5. upload file to radar-mandiri-sukses/public/uploads